{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, demographic and background information, including gender, age, department, and university affiliation, were collected on the scale form.",
    "The survey was administered in person to all accessible students over five months.",
    "Students were briefed on the study's objectives before participation, and voluntary consent forms were provided.",
    "Participation in the survey was strictly voluntary.",
    "Students were instructed to select the response option that best represented their views on the scale form."
  ]
}